Name: Post create booking
Description: POST call to create a new booking in the database

Name: Health check
Description: GET health check to confirm whether the API is up and running

Name: Workflow
Description: Different calls validations to change the status of a booking form created to deleted

Name: Get all booking id list
Description: GET call to retrieve all bookings id list

Name: Delete booking
Description: DELETE call to erase a booking in the database

Name: Get booking by id
Description: GET call to retrieve a booking by id

Name: Put update booking
Description: PUT call to update a booking in the database

Name: Patch partial update booking
Description: PATCH call to partially update a booking in the database
